Size Small (+1 AC, +1 attack rolls, +4 Hide, ¾ carrying capacity)
Speed 20 ft.
Ability Scores +2 Dexterity, +1 Charisma, –1 Strength
Vision Normal
Languages Automatic: Halfling. Bonus: Common, Aquan, Sylvan
Skill Bonuses +2 Climb, +2 Swim, +2 Move Silently
Spell-Like 1/day---create
