+1 every two levels (+5 at 9th). Arrows are magical only for the archer.
• Imbue Arrow (Sp): Place an area spell (e.g., gust of wind) on an arrow, centering the effect
where it lands (2nd). Standard action, must fire in same round.
• Seeker Arrow (Sp): 1/day, arrow seeks known target within range, negating
cover/concealment (4th). Standard action.

OREKA — Echoes of the Elemental Dawn
