OREKA — Echoes of the Elemental Dawn
82
Archmage
Archmages are emerging among Hasura and Na'wasua Elves, who study Deceiver spellbooks in
hidden groves. Their mastery of arcane magic, often air or twilight-based, promises to reshape
Oreka's magical landscape. They seek to restore Kin unity, wary of the Shattering's legacy.
Requirements
• Skills: Knowledge (arcana) 15 ranks, Spellcraft 15 ranks.
• Feats: Skill Focus (Spellcraft), Spell Focus (two schools), Elemental Affinity in Oreka.
• Spells: Ability to cast 7th-level arcane spells, know 5th-level+ spells from five schools.
Class Features
• Hit Die: d4.
• Class Skills: Concentration (Con), Craft (alchemy) (Int), Knowledge (all) (Int), Profession
(Wis), Search (Int), Spellcraft (Int) (2 + Int modifier skill points/level).
• Weapon and Armor Proficiency: No new proficiencies.
