vengeance at the Lament of Kings.
Blackguard
Blackguards, devotees of Hareem's darker aspects, are rare and feared. Taraf-Imro Humans and
Rarozhki Dwarves, driven by ambition or vengeance, embrace this path, wielding fire-based divine
magic. Their presence post-Deceivers' War deepens Kin divisions, clashing with paladins of Tarvek
Wen.
