• Water Sense: Detect creatures and disturbances within 30 ft. of any body of water (2nd).
• Summon Water Elemental: Summon a Medium water elemental as a standard action, 1/day
(3rd), 2/day (5th).
• Current Shield: As an immediate action, create a shield of swirling water granting +4
deflection to AC for 1 round, usable 3/day (4th).
Oreka Integration
Pekakarlik River Wardens patrol the Great River from Forkmeet to the sea, using their Riverborn
heritage to commune with water spirits. They are essential defenders of trade flotillas and often
serve as guides through the treacherous river narrows.

