Forge Mystic
Rarozhki Dwarves who blend smithing with divine magic become Forge Mystics, crafting
enchanted embersteel items. They channel divine energy through their forges, creating weapons
and armor infused with the Lord of Flame's power. Each piece they create carries a spark of
elemental fire.
Requirements
• Skills: Craft (Metal) 8 ranks.
• Spells: Ability to cast 2nd-level divine spells.
• Feats: Forge Mastery feat.
Class Features
• Hit Die: d8.
• Class Skills: Concentration (Con), Craft (Int), Knowledge (arcana, religion) (Int), Profession
(Wis), Spellcraft (Int) (2 + Int modifier skill points/level).
• Weapon and Armor Proficiency: All simple and martial weapons, all armor, shields.
